Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:06.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆前情回顾\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Previously on "Salem"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:08.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不管有没有你的帮助\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I will find Mercy Lewis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我都会找到默茜 路易斯\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}with or without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是说我是\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Are you saying that I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:15.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一个女巫\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}A witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:18.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,明天我会\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Tomorrow I shall bring
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,向委员会提交约翰 奥尔登的案子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}John Alden's case before the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他是无辜的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:24.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是知道的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,遵从因克里斯 麦哲的指令\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}By order of Increase Mather,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我宣布将你逮捕\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I place you under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我决定为奥尔登上尉辩护\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I've decided to defend Captain Alden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:36.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,辩护吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}To defend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:01:00.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让小孩子们都到我这里吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Let the little children come unto me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:06.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为魔鬼之国属于他们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}for the kingdom of the Devil belongs to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:07.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:10.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,坐这儿吧 可怜的孩子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Sit here, poor boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:14.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可怜的 可爱的小男孩 你帮家人工作而劳累致死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Poor, sweet boy, worked to death by your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:18.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你生命中的每日每夜\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Every day of your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:21.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,使你不配埋葬在墓地\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}making you unfit for burial in the churchyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:23.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以他们把你抛尸于此\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}so they dumped you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怀了舅父的孩子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Died in child birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:33.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,最后死于分娩\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}pregnant from your mother's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:36.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在那边 那儿 那个婴儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}There. There, the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:44.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,被闷死以隐藏证据\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Smothered to hide the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:50.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让母亲和孩子在一起吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Let mother and child be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:56.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在我就是你的母亲\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I am your mother now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:59.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们所有人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:01.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们都是我的孩子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And you all are my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我的父亲 深受尊敬的路易斯牧师\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}My father, the good Reverend Lewis,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说这世上没有炼狱\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}said that there is no purgatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:08.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,迷失在天堂和地狱之间的灵魂没有居所\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}no place for souls lost between heaven and hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:10.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是他错了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But he was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,地球就是炼狱\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Earth is purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:17.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们就是晃荡在这片土地上的鬼魂\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We are the ghosts that haunt this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:18.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 默茜\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No, Mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:21.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还好好的活着呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You are very much alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许比我们中的任何一个人都更活生生的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Perhaps more alive than any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:27.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是你像个幽灵一样隐藏了自己\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Yet you have hidden yourself like a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:30.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因克里斯在到处搜寻你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Increase searches everywhere for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他永远也不会找到这里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He will never look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是我的女孩们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But my girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:37.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我可怜的女孩们怎么办\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What of my poor girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:39.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他抓到了其中四个\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He has four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但你不用担心她们或你自己\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But do not fear for them or yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:45.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很快我们盛大的仪式将净化这片土地上的邪恶之事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Soon our grand rite will cleanse this land of the evil men do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,和行邪恶之事的邪恶之人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and the men who do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:49.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就像圣经时代的大洪水\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}like the great flood of biblical times,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为我们的新世界开路\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}making way for our new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,尽管放心吧 默茜\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And rest assured, Mercy --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:57.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你 你的女孩们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}you, your girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,和你的孩子们都会在那有立足之地\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and all your children shall have a place there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:05.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,噢 谢谢你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但告诉我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But tell me --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:13.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我 也许我就能消除她们的恐惧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}tell me so I may reassure them in their fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是什么事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,将要发生什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:28.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,死亡\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:22.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是一个古老的真理\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}'Tis an ancient proverbial truth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:26.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只要有一颗烂苹果在 就会烂掉一整筐\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}that it requires but one dead apple to rot an entire barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:29.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也渐渐相信只需一个烂苹果\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And I come to believe it requires but one apple
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:33.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就能让整片土地腐烂\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}to make this whole land equally rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但不是随便的哪颗苹果\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And not just any apple,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而是潘多拉魔盒\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}but the malum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,苹果的形状\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The icon of the apple
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:43.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,几乎贯穿了我们所见的有关盛大的仪式的每个画面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}runs through almost every image we have of the grand rite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,盛大的仪式带来了死亡\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The grand rite brings about death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:49.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,大规模死亡\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}death on a mass scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们对它的运作几乎都不了解\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We know little of its operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:53.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也不了解释放了随之而来的死亡\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}nor the -- the mechanism of magic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,的魔法的奥秘\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}that unleashes the -- the death that follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:00.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只有这一句莫明其妙又简单的话\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Only this one enigmatically simple sentence --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,魔盒开启\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}"Malum est aperta."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:07.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,邪恶降临\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}"The evil begins."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:09.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但这么多年我一直在误读\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But I have been misreading it all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们都理解错了 包括我的父亲\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We all have, my father included.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:14.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,魔盒的意思是邪恶 但同样也是苹果\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}"Malum" Means "Evil," But equally "Apple."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在我相信这个句子应该读做\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And I now believe the sentence to read,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.81,正片中文,,0,0,0,,苹果开启\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}"The apple opens,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:24.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,同时它又暗示 要释放其必然的结果 那就是死亡\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and, by implication, unleashes the death that results.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我相信我已经看到过那个苹果\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I believe I have seen that apple,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:30.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,或者说装着它的盒子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}or the box that contains it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:33.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在约翰 奥尔登的房子里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}In the house of John Alden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:40.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,麦哲牧师\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Reverend Mather?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道已经晚了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I know it is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你出来干什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What are you doing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道还能找谁\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I didn't know who else to turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是唯一一个可以帮我的人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You are the only one who can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 然后你就明智的来找我了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Well, then you did the right thing by coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:04.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,呃 我该怎样帮助你呢 还有帮你什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Uh...How may I help you, and -- and with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:07.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你认为 变成一个女巫\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Do you think it's possible to be a witch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而自己一点儿也不知道 可能吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and not even know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.36,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:13.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我 我认为一个人如果用其灵魂与撒旦结契\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I-I think one would know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他一定会知道的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}if one had...Deeded one's soul to Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那要是别人用你的灵魂结契了呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But what if someone deeded it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:21.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 黑尔小姐\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I can assure you, Miss Hale --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 我想要的不只是你的保证\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No. I want more than your assurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:26.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想要\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:33.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想让你现在就检查我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I want you to examine me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有没有魔鬼的标志\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}For the mark of the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后 你可以向我保证\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Then, you may assure me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我没找到撒旦的记号\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I feel no sign of Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在我看来 似乎 在每个方面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You seem, to me, in every respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:25.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都没受到魔鬼的烦扰\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}unmolested by the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 黑尔小姐\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I assure you, Miss Hale,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果你是一个女巫 你会知道的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}if you were a witch, you would know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不要问丧钟为谁而鸣\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Ask not for whom the bell tolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,它为\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It tolls for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想知道谁会是第一个\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I wonder who will be first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,会是谁呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Who will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,肯开口的人就不会被烧死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Whoever will speak will not burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,多简单\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:06.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,今晚这里真拥挤 不是吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Close in here this evening, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,想想我要去呼吸一下新鲜空气\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Think I'll take some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:13.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我离开以后 考虑一下\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}While I'm gone, consider...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:16.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谁第一个坦白\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Which of you will be the first to confess
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:20.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,巫师约翰 奥尔登对你们做了什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}what the witch John Alden did to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:39.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,默茜 感谢上帝\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Mercy, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们坚持不住了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}We cannot hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他要对我们逼供\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He is going to make us turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:46.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是你是要来拯救我们了吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But you have come to save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:48.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 那样不管用\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No, it doesn't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:52.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们还没准备好我的那种穿行\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You're not ready to travel as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:55.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但请记住 我们仍然为夜之女王服务\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But remember, we still serve the queen of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:59.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她比我还挂念你们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and she has not forgotten you any more than I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,会有那么一天 她会来拯救你们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and there will be a day where she will save you.
