Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是现在\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:08.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们必须给这老色鬼他想要的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}you must give that old goat what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:11.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我非常的害怕他想要的正是我们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm terribly afraid it's us he's going to serve up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:14.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这肯定是她计划的一部分\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}This is surely part of her design.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:17.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她的布局比我们的都庞大\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Her web is greater than all of ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而且她可以看到\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and she has a vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这片土地将要变成什么样子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}a vision of what this land could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以按照麦哲牧师说的做\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}So do as Reverend Mather asks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:26.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在审判时说不利于约翰 奥尔登的证词\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and speak against John Alden at the trial.
