Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,600)}没有什么能改变的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:55.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,魔盒开启\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Malum aperta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:01.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,718)}但为什么是约翰 奥尔登\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But why John Alden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,718)}但他是无辜的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But he is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,720)}这对我来说重要\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It matters to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,玛丽 听我说\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Mary, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:55.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,释放他就能知道你在他心中代表着什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}To free him would reveal what you are to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你认为他就会爱你了吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You think he could love you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:00.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不要失去他的爱\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Do not lose his love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:04.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,为了我们去利用它\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Use it for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:07.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这就是牺牲\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}That is the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:13.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在所有有关黑巫术的文献中\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}In all of the literature on witchcraft,
