Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.80,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以你告诉我为什么 就这个案子来讲\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}So you tell me why, in this particular case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:20.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,它应该代表苹果\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}should it signify "Apple"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:21.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我有理由相信这里所提的魔盒\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I have reason to believe the malum referred to here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:22.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是一个真实的事物\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}is an actual object,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,并且它就在塞勒姆 等着被用来对抗我们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and that object is here in Salem awaiting use against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:28.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 这真是一个有趣的定理\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Well, it's an interesting theorem,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:32.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是 这不符合理性思考的最基本的原则\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}but...It fails the most basic tenet of rational thinking.
