Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,-直线 -正确\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}- A line. - Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,常常\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And often,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:44.31,正片中文,,0,0,0,,最简单的解释正是最正确的解释\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}the simplest explanation is the correct explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:47.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想阻止盛大仪式\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm only trying to stop the grand rite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,阻止盛大的仪式吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Stop the grand rite?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:54.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我的儿啊 年少轻狂啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Oh, my, the arrogance of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那你知道如何阻止吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Would you even know how to stop it?
