Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:15.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你还只是个婴儿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You were still just a-a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:16.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,德国巫师 哦\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The German witches, oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:19.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,远远比埃塞克斯巫师更为猖狂\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}far bolder than even the essex witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:23.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们企图举行盛大的仪式\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}They attempted the grand rite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:28.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一个月内 十二个孩子消失了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Within the space of a month, a dozen children disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们的尸体被发现时已血尽干枯\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Their bodies were found bled dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:34.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们无辜的血浸湿了地面\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Their innocent blood soaked the ground.
