Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:48.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么这么大胆\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.47,0:23:50.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 先生 你怎么这么大胆\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No, sir! How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:59.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这场庭审今天暂停\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}This session is suspended for the day!
