Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.21,0:27:44.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,怕得要死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Deathly afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.41,0:27:47.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我怕 尽管我们所用的方法不同\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I fear, while we disagree on methods,
