Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.22,0:27:58.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你至少承认了这点\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm gratified that you at least acknowledge that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.13,0:28:04.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,盒子在这里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The malum is here.
