Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.02,0:28:25.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我你在哪看见的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Tell me where you saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.06,0:28:31.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在约翰 奥尔登的房子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}In John Alden's house.
