Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.37,0:29:20.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在某些方面 女巫和我们不一样\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}In some respects, the witches are not unlike us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.64,0:29:24.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们有派系 他们有权力斗争\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}They have factions. They have power struggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.04,0:29:27.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你的朋友奥尔登不是在试图抓住女巫\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Your friend Alden was not trying to catch a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.55,0:29:29.51,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他只是在消除竞争对手\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He was eliminating a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.51,0:29:32.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你被你自己的疑问蒙蔽了双眼\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You are blinded by your own doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.62,0:29:35.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这会毁了你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and it will destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.19,0:29:36.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我同意你的话\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}If I grant you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.49,0:29:40.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那就有一种可能奥尔登是无罪的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}that there is a possibility that Alden is innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.06,0:29:42.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你就不能承认这种\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}can you not grant the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.06,0:29:44.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,十分之一 不 百分之一的可能性\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}that there is a 1 in 10, nay, a 1 in 100 chance
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.83,0:29:47.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我是对的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}that I am right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.07,0:29:49.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果我是对的 数千人将灭亡\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And if I am, thousands will perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.84,0:29:51.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,国家会衰落\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The nation itself may fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.47,0:29:53.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你能承担那种可能性吗 我不能\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Can we take that chance? I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.54,0:29:55.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你能吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.64,0:29:57.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 柯顿\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I tell you, Cotton,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.04,0:29:59.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不知道这个男人几乎也是你认为你所做的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}you do not know this man nearly as well as you think you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.48,0:30:02.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我搜查了吉尔斯科里的坟墓\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I searched Giles Corey's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.38,0:30:03.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,盒子不在那里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The malum wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.82,0:30:06.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那不可能 是我亲手埋了它的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}That's impossible. I buried it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.49,0:30:08.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有谁看见了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Who else knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.12,0:30:10.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.02,0:30:11.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只有你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.09,0:30:17.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而且你不相信我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And you don't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.06,0:30:19.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道该相信什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm not sure what to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.97,0:30:21.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我只相信两样东西\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I am certain only of two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.67,0:30:23.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们一生也许就寄托在\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}All our lives may depend on
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.07,0:30:25.20,正片中文,,0,0,0,,找到并销毁那盒子上\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}finding and destroying the malum.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.20,0:30:27.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.61,0:30:29.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还有你对我更加不坦诚了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And you are being less than honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.51,0:30:34.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我已经把一切都告诉你了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I've told you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.62,0:30:42.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,到底还要说什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.72,0:30:44.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,醒醒吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}- Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.96,0:30:46.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那些女孩是无辜的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Those girls are innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.43,0:30:49.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.47,0:30:55.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,原谅我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.63,0:30:58.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那是我唯一后悔的事 对你撒谎\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's the only thing I regret -- lying about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.64,0:31:00.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看 我知道他们对你做了什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Look, I know what they did to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.91,0:31:01.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那不是你的错\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.94,0:31:03.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,来我这\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.84,0:31:07.28,正片中文,,0,0,0,,去你妈的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.28,0:31:09.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,做些什么吧她们只是群女孩子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Do something! They're just girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.98,0:31:43.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你 你答应过会饶恕我们的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You! You promised you'd spare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.69,0:31:49.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个世界我将用火结束你的生命\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I am sparing you the flames of this world
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.69,0:31:51.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,下个世界你还是要受到火的炼狱\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and of the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.12,0:31:54.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你不会痛苦太久的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You will not suffer long.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.33,0:31:59.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我将会给你腿上戴上宽恕的铁链\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}A full measure of Mercy is being added to your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.43,0:32:00.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,放我过去\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.60,0:32:02.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,父亲 你撒了谎\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Father, you lied!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.27,0:32:04.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你答应过这些女孩会\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You promised these girls they wouldn't --
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.47,0:32:05.90,正片中文,,0,0,0,,点火\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.90,0:32:07.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,没有人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Nor shall they.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.14,0:32:08.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,别这样 父亲\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Don't do this, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.37,0:32:10.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这会有帮助吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How can this possibly help?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.74,0:32:12.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你过说她们都是受害者\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You said yourself they were victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.58,0:32:13.75,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很遗憾但是是事实\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Sad but true.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.75,0:32:16.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但她们被感染了 被女巫\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But they're tainted... By the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.58,0:32:18.88,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我恐怕她们带走了他的种子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I fear they carry his very seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.88,0:32:20.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么那么肯定\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How can you be certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.19,0:32:21.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我很肯定\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I am certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.35,0:32:24.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我肯定这个威胁是指向塞勒姆的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I am certain of the threat they pose to Salem,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.09,0:32:27.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就像我肯定你的软弱构成了威胁\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}just as I am certain that your weakness poses a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.19,0:32:30.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但总之 我很肯定\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But above all, I am certain that,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.53,0:32:33.73,正片中文,,0,0,0,,就像一个外科医生 我别无选择只能切除\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}like a surgeon, I have no choice but to cut out
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.73,0:32:36.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,恶性肿瘤\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}the malignant manifestation of malice
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.27,0:32:38.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在它进一步扩散之前\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}before it can spread any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.81,0:32:41.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 停下\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.87,0:32:44.14,正片中文,,0,0,0,,请帮帮我 求你了 求你了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Please help me! Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.14,0:32:45.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,回去\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.23,0:33:06.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,点火\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Burn in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.87,0:33:08.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,让她们燃烧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Let them burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.85,0:33:47.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,默茜\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.78,0:33:50.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你在哪里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.99,0:33:53.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,默茜\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.42,0:33:55.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.52,0:33:57.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,多利 发生什么了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Dollie, what has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.83,0:34:03.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,艾米丽 伊丽莎白 苏珊娜 和\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Emily, Elizabeth, Susanna, and charity --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.00,0:34:05.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因克里斯麦哲把她们都绞死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Increase Mather has hung them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.41,0:34:13.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你发誓她们会安全的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You swore that they would be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.57,0:34:14.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但现在她们死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}but they're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.68,0:34:16.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,她们所有人都死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}All of them have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.64,0:34:18.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你说过你的主人会保护我们的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You said your master would protect us,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.91,0:34:20.21,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但她什么都没做\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and she did nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.42,0:34:26.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,回到塞勒姆吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Go back to Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.62,0:34:28.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,把年轻人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Gather the young,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.46,0:34:33.49,正片中文,,0,0,0,,穷人和受苦的人聚集起来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}the poor, the suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.49,0:34:37.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们会成为我们的军队\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}They will be our army.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.17,0:34:39.77,正片中文,,0,0,0,,新的一天就在我们眼前\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}A new day is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.77,0:34:41.97,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但新的一天需要\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And that new day demands
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.97,0:34:45.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一个新的黑夜女王\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}a new queen of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.18,0:34:51.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你们很多人觉得这难以接受\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I know that so many of you find it hard to accept,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.35,0:34:54.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不敢相信约翰奥尔登\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}impossible to believe that John Alden,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.42,0:34:59.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们造物者的一个儿子 一个勇敢的战士为了保护我们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}son of one of our founders and a brave soldier in our defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.02,0:35:02.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为邪恶的巫术而有罪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}is guilty of malefic witchcraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.76,0:35:04.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.43,0:35:05.89,正片中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.89,0:35:09.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不管你们抛弃不抛弃你们的信仰 这都不重要\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Suspend your belief or not. It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.10,0:35:16.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只有一件事是重要的 那就是 奥尔登被判是有罪的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The only thing that matters is that Alden...Be convicted
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.34,0:35:19.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,事实上他\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and sentenced for what he truly is,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.61,0:35:22.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是一个叛徒和杀人犯\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}a traitor and a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.58,0:35:24.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.08,0:35:25.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.48,0:35:30.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我认为尽管奥尔登一直和印第安人在一起\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I submit that while John Alden was with the Indians,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.95,0:35:33.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,而且不只是和他们一起共事\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}he not only took up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.55,0:35:37.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他建立起了反对他们自己人的军队\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He took up arms against his own people,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.19,0:35:41.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在自己的国家屠宰民兵\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}slaughtering militiamen in his own company,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.23,0:35:45.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,善良的新英格兰人 每个人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}good new england men, every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.33,0:35:48.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我发誓这是真的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I swear this to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.57,0:35:52.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我恐怕约翰奥尔登会否认这些事实\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And I dare John Alden to deny it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.44,0:35:54.64,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我恐怕你不敢告诉我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I dare you to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.64,0:35:59.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你把自己的脸化成一个印第安异教徒\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}that you did not paint your face as a heathen Indian
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.95,0:36:03.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,并且在你自己的国家粉碎人的头骨\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and smash the skulls of men in your own company!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.25,0:36:05.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,胡说八道\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Outrageous accusations!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.52,0:36:08.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你到底是怎么说出这些胡话的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Wherever did you find such nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.09,0:36:11.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我发誓这些证词来自奴隶缇图芭\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I have sworn testimony from the slave Tituba!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.03,0:36:12.63,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哼\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.63,0:36:15.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,全是谎话和幻想\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Lies and fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.53,0:36:17.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,谎话 上尉\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Lies? Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.67,0:36:20.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,幻想\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Fantasies?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.17,0:36:23.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你想申辩吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Do you dispute the charges?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.61,0:36:26.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.08,0:36:32.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,上尉 这些都是真的吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Captain...Is this all true?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.92,0:36:39.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在这里每一个理智尚存的人都知道我不是巫师\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Every sane man in this place knows I ain't a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.95,0:36:43.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是背叛者吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Are you a traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.19,0:36:45.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是杀人犯吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Are you a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.43,0:36:50.86,正片中文,,0,0,0,,混蛋 约翰 快回答他啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Damn you, John. Answer him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.51,0:37:05.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那么 大家看见了吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}So, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.38,0:37:10.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有时候 沉默就是最有说服力的认罪\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Sometimes, silence can be the most eloquent confession of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.52,0:37:15.12,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我从不怀疑 没有一丝一毫怀疑过\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I have no doubt, not a sliver of a doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.12,0:37:17.26,正片中文,,0,0,0,,约翰 奥尔登是一个巫师\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}that John Alden is a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.26,0:37:22.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是 既是我不是必须这么做\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But...Even had I not...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.40,0:37:24.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我还是坚持\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I would still maintain
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.03,0:37:30.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,要为了他无法否认的罪行 施以绞刑\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}that he must hang for crimes he will not deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.87,0:37:34.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你们也应该这么想\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And nor should you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.65,0:37:41.68,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上 告诉我 我父亲说错了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}For God's sake, tell me my father is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.68,0:37:44.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,告诉我 你不是他说的那样的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Tell me you are not the man he says you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.65,0:37:45.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这现在还重要吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What does it matter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.99,0:37:48.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对我来说很重要\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It matters to me --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.82,0:37:50.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你到底有没有愚弄我这么久\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}whether you duped me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.52,0:37:54.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你确定你想要真相吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Are you sure you want the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.46,0:37:55.66,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你真他妈的确定\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Are you really damn sure
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.66,0:37:58.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道善与恶的区别吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}you know the difference between good and evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.17,0:38:00.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为你是个清教徒\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}'Cause you puritans,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.07,0:38:04.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你会觉得世界上不是黑就是白\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}you think the world is just black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.17,0:38:08.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但如果这世界的真相就是灰色的呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What if the truth of the world is that it's nothing but gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.18,0:38:16.65,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在大沼泽之战之后\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}After the battle of the great swamp,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.65,0:38:20.19,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我生死不明被所有人抛弃了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I was left for dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.19,0:38:23.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是我被莫霍克人所找到\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But I was found by the mohawk --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.99,0:38:26.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是跟我们打仗的那些印第安人 不\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}not the Indians we fought, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.46,0:38:28.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,莫霍克人不是我们的盟友\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The mohawk aren't our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.70,0:38:33.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是他们是与我们打仗的阿布纳基人的敌人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}but they are the enemies of the abenaki we fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.47,0:38:38.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,说实在的 我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}In all honesty, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.04,0:38:44.11,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不认为我能理解他们为什么会救我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I don't think I'll ever understand why they saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.11,0:38:47.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,直到现在对我来说都是个迷\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It is a mystery to me to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.32,0:38:53.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你父亲找到的伤疤\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The scar your old man found
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.42,0:38:55.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他说是喂养一个奴仆所留下的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}he said was from feeding a familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.79,0:38:57.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那其实是是从我身体里取出铅弹\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}That was from digging a ball of lead out of me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.42,0:39:00.06,正片中文,,0,0,0,,并且用他们的药治愈我留下的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and healing it with their medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.06,0:39:03.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们留下你要求赎金吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}They held you for ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.00,0:39:05.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.00,0:39:07.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们用善意和尊敬对待我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}They treated me with kindness and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.30,0:39:11.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们的圣人对我很感兴趣\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And their holy men took an interest in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.41,0:39:14.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我都不确定为什么 或是他在透过我看见了什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm not even sure why or what he saw in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.34,0:39:16.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但如果不是他\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}but if he hadn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.54,0:39:18.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我早就死了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.55,0:39:22.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所以我在他们之间生活\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}So I lived amongst them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.18,0:39:24.98,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我分享了他们的食物和庇护\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I shared their food and their shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.99,0:39:26.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我甚至和他们一起打猎\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I even hunted with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.69,0:39:30.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有一天 我和几个勇者打猎回来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}One day, me and a few braves returned from a hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.32,0:39:34.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,发现整个村子都被烧成了灰烬只剩下废墟\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}to find the village had been burned to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.23,0:39:37.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,女人和孩子们 都散落在村庄各地\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The women and the children, they're all scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.47,0:39:42.13,正片中文,,0,0,0,,像是死了的、飘落的树叶 他们被屠杀了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}like dead, fallen leaves, slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.14,0:39:44.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,被阿布纳基人吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}By the abenaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.10,0:39:45.57,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.57,0:39:48.41,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是军队\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Militia.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.41,0:39:51.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们的军队\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Our militia.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.85,0:39:53.18,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们从不屑于\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Couldn't even be bothered
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.18,0:39:55.45,正片中文,,0,0,0,,分辨不同的印第安人的村落\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}to tell one Indian tribe from another.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.45,0:39:58.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,血红色的雾从我心中升起\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}A red fog descended upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.82,0:40:00.99,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这雾不曾消散 直到我穿过树林\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and it did not lift until I ran through those woods
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.99,0:40:03.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,杀死了所有那些混蛋\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and killed every one of those bastards,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.56,0:40:05.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所有人 除了我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}everyone but one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.10,0:40:12.50,正片中文,,0,0,0,,对于那件事 我要纠正的是 就是那晚我找到了盒子\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And that I corrected the night I found the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.31,0:40:22.71,正片中文,,0,0,0,,潘多拉之盒吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And the malum?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.61,0:40:25.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我对它一无所知\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I didn't know nothing about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.48,0:40:30.42,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你说那就是女巫们一直渴望得到的东西\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You said it was something that the witches wanted badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.42,0:40:32.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,当我们在树林里跟丢了那个女巫的时候\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}When we lost that witch in the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.02,0:40:33.92,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想到最好还是把它藏起来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I thought it was best to hide it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.92,0:40:36.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,所有 就像我告诉你的那样 我把它和吉尔斯一起埋了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}so, like I told you, I buried it with Giles.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.32,0:40:37.76,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那么 就是其他人又把它拿了出来\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Well, then someone unburied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.76,0:40:39.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许你什么也不必担心\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Maybe you have nothing to worry about, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.43,0:40:40.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,因为照你父亲所说\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}because according to your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.70,0:40:42.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我就是幕后的巫师\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I am the witch behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.96,0:40:45.33,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你唯一要做的就是绞死我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}So, all you have to do is hang me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.33,0:40:48.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后一切都会变好的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and then everything will be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.07,0:40:50.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不能理解的是\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What I can't figure out,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.67,0:40:54.67,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我想要推测的是\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}what I am trying to surmise,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.68,0:40:57.91,正片中文,,0,0,0,,过了这么久\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}is, after all of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.91,0:41:01.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,经过了我们所遇见的一切\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}after everything we've been through --
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.72,0:41:06.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是需要一个朋友 还是一个兵卒\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}you needed a friend or a pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.39,0:41:26.96,正片中文,,0,0,0,,哭泣什么忙也帮不了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Weeping don't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.96,0:41:28.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.60,0:41:30.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我做了我应该做的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Done my fair share.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.60,0:41:37.24,正片中文,,0,0,0,,以撒\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.24,0:41:39.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,上帝啊 你还在流血\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}God, you're still bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.27,0:41:41.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在这里 谁不会呢\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Around here, who ain't?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.35,0:41:52.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我到底做了什么\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.56,0:41:59.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我知道这些都不是你的错\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I know none of this is your fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.23,0:42:00.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都是我的错\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and all of it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.56,0:42:03.10,正片中文,,0,0,0,,那天他正要离开镇上\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}He was on his way out of town that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.10,0:42:04.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是我阻止了他\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I stopped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.17,0:42:05.93,正片中文,,0,0,0,,如果不是我的话 他早就离开了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}If it weren't for me, he'd be long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.93,0:42:07.43,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这些事都不会发生了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}None of this would have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.44,0:42:11.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也许明天早上还得是我拉绳子绞死他\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I might as well pull the rope myself in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.34,0:42:15.74,正片中文,,0,0,0,,还是我杀死了约翰 奥尔登\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I've as good as killed John Alden.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.74,0:42:17.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但是你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.78,0:42:19.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你可以救他\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You can save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.55,0:42:22.22,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不能 我不能\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I can't. I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.22,0:42:23.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是玛丽\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You're Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.62,0:42:27.56,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是玛丽啊\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You're Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.56,0:42:28.72,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们叫你玛丽 西布里\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}They all call you Mary Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.72,0:42:30.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你知道我怎么叫你吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Do you know what I call you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.29,0:42:34.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,在我脑中 对我自己 心灵深处\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}in my head, to myself, in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.23,0:42:35.40,正片中文,,0,0,0,,神奇玛丽\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}"Magic Mary."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.40,0:42:38.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你总是很神奇\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You were always magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.60,0:42:41.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,即使我们都还是小豆芽菜的时候\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}even back when we was just sprouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.54,0:42:43.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你无所不能\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And you could do anything --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.47,0:42:45.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一直如此\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}always could.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.94,0:42:48.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你只需要等到事态变得一团糟\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You just have to want it bad enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.48,0:42:51.01,正片中文,,0,0,0,,然后你再出场\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.01,0:42:53.05,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不是吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.05,0:42:55.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你确实希望约翰 奥尔登活着\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You do want John Alden to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.61,0:43:26.78,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你是怎么进来的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.88,0:43:30.79,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们明天就会把你绞死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}They will hang you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.79,0:43:33.25,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}"They"?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.25,0:43:36.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 你难道不也是其中之一嘛  西布利女士\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Well, aren't you one of them, Mrs. Sibley?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.00,0:43:43.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,有的时候  我也不记得我是谁\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Sometimes, I no longer remember who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.60,0:43:45.83,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我知道你是谁\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But I know who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.83,0:43:48.27,正片中文,,0,0,0,,一个无辜的人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}an innocent man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.27,0:43:51.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,正相反\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.37,0:43:54.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这真是让人哭笑不得\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Now it's almost funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.58,0:43:57.34,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆终于给真真正正犯罪的人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Salem finally sentenced someone to die
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.35,0:43:59.55,正片中文,,0,0,0,,判下了死刑\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}for something they've actually done.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.55,0:44:02.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,回家吧 玛丽\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Go home, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.62,0:44:05.69,正片中文,,0,0,0,,过你自己的生活去  西布利夫人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Go back to your life, Mrs. Sibley.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.39,0:44:10.62,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你就是我的生活\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You are my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.23,0:44:16.46,正片中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 现在似乎有点晚了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Well, it's a little late for that thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.46,0:44:18.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不会让你上绞刑架的\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'll not let you hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.93,0:44:20.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我可以救你\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I can save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.60,0:44:22.00,正片中文,,0,0,0,,塞勒姆的好人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}The good people of Salem,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.00,0:44:25.61,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也就是那些我曾试图拯救的人\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}the people I've been trying to save,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.61,0:44:29.08,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们都想让我死\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}they all want me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.08,0:44:31.15,正片中文,,0,0,0,,他们认为我就是恶魔的本体\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}They think I'm the Devil himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.05,0:44:34.58,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我不是恶魔\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm no Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.25,0:44:42.02,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我确实为背叛而感到愧疚\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But I am guilty of treason...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.02,0:44:43.39,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也包括谋杀\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.53,0:44:48.03,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我已经做好了为此上绞刑架的准备\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And I'm ready to hang for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.90,0:44:52.87,正片中文,,0,0,0,,况且\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.87,0:44:54.30,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我也心累了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I'm awfully tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.60,0:44:57.54,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不能和你一起活着 很累\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Tired of living without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.54,0:45:00.07,正片中文,,0,0,0,,总有办法能使我们继续在一起\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}There's still a way for us to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.08,0:45:01.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,已经结束了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.04,0:45:02.44,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你哪根筋搭错了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.44,0:45:05.48,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你跟镇里的其他人一样都疯了吗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Have you gone mad like everyone else in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.48,0:45:08.52,正片中文,,0,0,0,,约翰 我向你保证\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}John, I promise you --
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.52,0:45:10.82,正片中文,,0,0,0,,不 别说什么保证\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}No, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.82,0:45:14.09,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们俩都不是会信守承诺的人  所以别信誓旦旦了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Neither of us is very good with promises, so no more vows.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.09,0:45:15.16,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你听我说\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.16,0:45:17.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我在听\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}I am listening to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.33,0:45:20.29,正片中文,,0,0,0,,可你说的都是无稽之谈\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}and you aren't making any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.30,0:45:23.60,正片中文,,0,0,0,,看看周围\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.60,0:45:27.70,正片中文,,0,0,0,,都是石头做得四壁\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}These are stone walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.70,0:45:29.17,正片中文,,0,0,0,,封掉的窗\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Barred windows,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.17,0:45:31.47,正片中文,,0,0,0,,铁做得门\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}an iron door.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.47,0:45:35.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,现在我们头顶上悬着一根粗绳子 分分钟要我命\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Right above us, a thick rope awaiting my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.94,0:45:39.38,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这是铁的事实\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Those are the stubborn facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.38,0:45:40.35,正片中文,,0,0,0,,即使爱得多深\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}And all the love in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.35,0:45:42.95,正片中文,,0,0,0,,也不能改变现在的这种局面 哪怕一点点\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}can't change a single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.95,0:45:44.32,正片中文,,0,0,0,,你错了\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.32,0:45:48.59,正片中文,,0,0,0,,爱比现实更强大  爱无坚不摧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Love is stronger than fact, stronger than everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.53,0:45:53.23,正片中文,,0,0,0,,但我告诉你 约翰\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}But I tell you, John,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.23,0:45:56.53,正片中文,,0,0,0,,这个世界上还是有这么块属于我们的地方\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}there is still a place for us in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.53,0:45:59.37,正片中文,,0,0,0,,只有在梦里才有\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Only in dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.37,0:46:01.84,正片中文,,0,0,0,,行 那就这样吧\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.84,0:46:05.04,正片中文,,0,0,0,,最后一次\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}One last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.04,0:46:06.94,正片中文,,0,0,0,,我们一起入梦\N{\3c&H0000000&\fs30}Dream with me.
